snippet.title: Helldivers 2 - Bile Titan Liberation Gameplay | PS5 & PC Games
snippet.description:
Bile Titan takedown mission in progress. This gameplay is classified. 

Join Johan Pilestedt and the Arrowhead Game Studio in a closer look at Helldivers 2 mission gameplay. Watch them take on a deadly Bile Titan using only their bare highly powered weaponry. This is only the beginning of our war against the enemies of Managed Democracy.

Join the Helldivers and fight for freedom with friends across a hostile galaxy in this fast, frantic third-person co-op shooter. 

Available February 8, 2024 on PS5 and Steam!
Pre-order from 1am PST September 22.

#ps5 #ps5games #helldivers #stateofplay 

Rated Mature
